Importing an aPi using Open Api
select the apim resource ---> apis --> openapi --> add an api ,give details
The apim will hit the backend api

Apim distinguish apis by using suffix so it should be unique
Apim isntance comes with 2 sample products ,, 1 starter and unlimted

You publish an api by associating it with the product

Authentication types with ApimDifferent
OAuth2.0
Basic Authentication
Mutual Tls
